## §0 Terminal goal — universal fusion-energy substrate (D-T → p-¹¹B → KSTAR-N6)

hexa-fusion 도착지 = **27/27 EXACT (현재 26/27, lawson_triple 1-decade gap 잔존) + 12-archetype closure 122/122 자동 회귀 + p-¹¹B aneutronic 1m³ 시뮬레이션 wired + KSTAR-N6 powerplant Q≥10 closed-form 검증**.

DoD:
1. `fusion_ledger` 27/27 EXACT (lawson_triple 1-decade gap resolved 또는 documented falsifier).
2. 12-fusion-archetype closure 122/122 EXACT 자동 회귀 (cycle-bound test).
3. `tabletop_fusion` p-¹¹B aneutronic 1m³ 시뮬레이션 wired (.hexa).
4. `fusion_powerplant` KSTAR-N6 RT-SC coil 48T → Q=σ-φ=10 closed-form 검증.

n=6 invariant lattice (§A.1) 는 도착지의 *correctness machinery* — 도착지 자체가 아닌 closed-form 정합성 보장 도구.

## §A.1 Invariant lattice (n=6)

```
σ(6) · φ(6) = n · τ(6) = J₂ = 24
   12   ·   2  =  6  ·   4  = 24
```

| Symbol | Value | Role | Fusion projection |
|--------|-------|------|-------------------|
| σ(6)   | 12    | sigma — cardinality bin | 12 fusion archetypes / 12 ITER constants stratum |
| τ(6)   | 4     | tau — state quartet | Q-gain = τ = 4 (TTF conservative break-even) |
| φ(6)   | 2     | phi — verdict bit | aneutronic / DT-neutronic |
| J₂     | 24    | Mathieu / Leech | σ·φ = n·τ = 24 master identity |

Master identity: **σ·φ = n·τ = J₂ = 24**. Q-gain = σ-φ = 10 (powerplant). T_i = σ+φ = 14 keV (plasma core). B = σ·τ = 48 T (SC coil).

